metadata.name: The one who is always behind me
metadata.description:
The depicted girl embodies the essence of purity, vulnerability and unbridled emotion. She stands as beacons of strength, transcending the boundaries of social norms and embracing the depths of her being. Nevertheless, she is not alone in this journey.
The demon represents a mysterious and otherworldly presence. It represents the hidden aspects of the psyche, the unrestrained desires and inner struggles we all face. This demon serves as a protector and guide, helping the girl on her journey of self-discovery and growth. It symbolizes the transformative power that comes from confronting and embracing the inner darkness.
